{"type": "article", "id": 12860, "title": "阿富汗／日本主题织绒地毯", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-31T07:34:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606060002130vGARPXQtwxkrSMe.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t近日，西班牙艺术家 Jaime Hayon 与意大利奢侈毯子品牌 Nodus 合作，推出了两款织绒地毯，分别叫做 “阿富汗传说”和”日本传说”。正如其名字显示的，这两款毯子的灵感来源都是阿富汗与日本民间的传说和神话故事。作者通过与两国当地手工艺人的合作，在制作地毯的过程中探索两国的文化，辅以 Nodus 精湛的工艺，试图把传统文化和现代技术融合在一起，也能让西方感受来自东方的文化。毯子的设计精巧而又充满细节，对两国文化感兴趣的可以<a href=\"http://www.hayonstudio.com/design/afghan-folklore-for-nodus/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>关注更多。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140549nt2JKXmc17fWIbCR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140550TENfXBrj7Ic3ZPhJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261405509imV5zARdxk8up3Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261405517pmvIoRaL5EUFXSl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140553IWb5yGQ2Ez8AiCf1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140553Hga6C3nfJVQvLexp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}